   Write a program that will solve a quadratic equation of the form x^2 + bx + c = 0.
   ~~~~
   a = 1
   # write code to prompt the user to enter b (linear coefficient))
   # write code to prompt the user to enter c (constant term))
   # write code that uses the formulas to calculate the 2 roots and places them two variables  
   # write code that prints the 2 variables with an explanation